        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "8. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hisham ibn Salim who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Circumcision is of pure obedience to Allah.’” "
